PluginInformation
public static enum PluginInformation.Information
extends java.lang.Enum<PluginInformation.Information>

The set of information item that can be requested. S1 means a list of strings with exactly one element is returnd, S+ means a number of strings will be returned. In case no information was available an empty collection is returned.

Author:
Ralf Biedert
